</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>日本 Apple 取消外國人退稅政策，赴日買 iPhone、Mac 需繳足消費稅</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/26/appletaxfree/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=appletaxfree</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Natalie]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jun 2022 02:18:03 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[退稅]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1106354</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>現時日元已經跌穿 6 算，創 20 年新低，雖然現時疫情仍未穩定，但相信一定有很多港人已經兌換大批日元，待稍後 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">現時日元已經跌穿 6 算，創 20 年新低，雖然現時疫情仍未穩定，但相信一定有很多港人已經兌換大批日元，待稍後「返鄉下」使用。不過，現時日本 Apple Store 實行了新政策，非日本居民購買 Apple 產品時不能再退稅。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106358" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.12.54-PM-694x503.png" alt="" width="694" height="503" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.12.54-PM-694x503.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.12.54-PM-768x557.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.12.54-PM.png 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2206/21/news176.html">IT Media News</a></span></p><p>日本 Apple Store 作為「Japan Tax-free Shop」的一部份，在特定店鋪對於外國人以特定方式購買產品，可享有退稅優惠。<span style="font-weight: 400;">但日前日本 Apple Store 宣佈，在 6 月 21 日開始，取消外國遊客等的非日本居民購買 Apple 產品時享有的退稅優惠，換言之，即是現時到日本 Apple Store 購買產品時不可以再退稅。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1106356" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.13.04-PM-559x580.png" alt="" width="559" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.13.04-PM-559x580.png 559w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.13.04-PM-867x900.png 867w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.13.04-PM-768x797.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Screenshot-2022-06-22-at-5.13.04-PM.png 1174w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 559px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2206/21/news176.html">IT Media News</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">有日本媒體估計，日本 Apple Store 實施這項政策有機會是避免有外國人因為日元匯率持續下跌，有利可圖之下將日本購得的貨品在外國轉售。</span></p><p>不過在日本，除了 Apple Store 之外，好多大型電器店都有賣 iPhone 產品，例如 BicCamera、Yodobashi 等等，用家仍然有可能在日本當地購買 iPhone 等 Apple 產品而獲得退稅。</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.itmedia.co.jp/news/articles/2206/21/news176.html">IT Media News</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">圖片來源：<a href="https://appleinsider.com/articles/20/09/04/japan-antitrust-regulator-to-increase-scrutiny-of-apples-app-store">Apple Insider</a></span></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
